Author: bestrongandfast
Text: You’re not alone ❤️ I feel exactly the same. Idk when food started ruling my life to this degree. Today I felt so depressed just because I had been restricting well for 3 days and had a NORMAL PORTIONED, HEALTHY AND NUTRITIOUS, VEGAN breakfast. It literally ruined my day and I don’t know why. And now I’m obsessed with thinking about “starting over” tomorrow
